Tuition Link: A bachelor degree with a 2:1 (hons) in a subject containing a substantial mathematical and statistical component.  Successful applicants will have a foundation in Statistics including strong grades in statistical modules. We may ask for further detailed module information if these are not clear on your transcript. We do not normally accept degrees in Accountancy or Finance.
